00:40:49.210 --> 00:40:56.480
is? See, what happened was Dorothy Sayers
fell in love with Peter Wimsey. She created

00:40:56.480 --> 00:41:04.180
him, she created the whole world that he was
in and she also saw he was horribly lonely,

00:41:04.180 --> 00:41:09.470
and she wanted to get into that world and
